29#include <gelf.h>
30#include <libelf.h>
31
32#include "_libelf.h"
33
34__RCSID("$NetBSD: libelf_shdr.c,v 1.3 2016/02/20 02:43:42 christos Exp $");
35ELFTC_VCSID("Id: libelf_shdr.c 3174 2015-03-27 17:13:41Z emaste ");
36
37void *
38_libelf_getshdr(Elf_Scn *s, int ec)
39{
40 Elf *e;
41
42 if (s == NULL || (e = s->s_elf) == NULL ||
43 e->e_kind != ELF_K_ELF) {
44 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
45 return (NULL);
46 }
47
48 if (ec == ELFCLASSNONE)
49 ec = e->e_class;
50
51 if (ec != e->e_class) {
52 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(CLASS, 0);
53 return (NULL);
54 }
55
56 return ((void *) &s->s_shdr);
57}
